  li = 0.

  FIND LAST rfq {&where-first1} USE-INDEX rfq NO-LOCK NO-ERROR.
  DO WHILE AVAIL rfq:
    IF rfq.rfq-no NE lv-rfq-no THEN li = li + 1.
